Beacon Roofing Supply, Inc. (NASDAQ: BECN) is an American publicly traded company which sells residential and non-residential roofing products, as well as related building products in North America. The company currently consist of 13 regional companies in 48 states and 6 Canadian Provinces, 384 locations and over 5,000 employees.[4] In addition to roofing, local divisions may also sell windows, siding, decking, waterproofing, and other external building products. [5][6] The company is currently headquartered in Herndon, Virginia.[7]



